content:
Salesforce Messaging offers a variety of experiences. You can add messaging to your mobile app or website with Messaging for In-App and Web, connect third-party messaging apps such as WhatsApp, or integrate your preferred messaging service with Bring Your Own Channel.

Messaging for In-App and Web:
Available in Lightning Experience only
Available in Enterprise Edition for Service Cloud with the Digital Engagement add-on license
Available in Enterprise Edition for Sales Cloud with the Sales Engagement add-on license
Available in Unlimited Edition for Service and Sales Cloud
Available in Developer Edition

Messaging for WhatsApp, Facebook Messenger, Apple Messages for Business, and SMS:
Available in Lightning Experience only
Available in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer Editions for Service Cloud or Sales Cloud with the Digital Engagement add-on license
Outbound messaging in WhatsApp is available with the WhatsApp Outbound Messages add-on license
SMS short code channels are available with the Short Codes add-on license
Not supported in Government Cloud Plus

Bring Your Own Channel:
Available in Lightning Experience only
Available in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer Editions for Service Cloud or Sales Cloud with the Digital Engagement add-on license
title: Messaging Editions in Service Cloud
